translations.name: The Bible in Anuak
translations.description: The Anuak church in Ethiopia is growing, and since only the New Testament and portions of the Old Testament have been translated, the demand for scripture has increased for the language’s 89,000 speakers. The New Testament and other Bible portions have been made available by the Ethiopian Bible Society since the year 2000.
